<br>
You are at one of the lowest points in a Mage's career.   32~33 are tough levels.  Old DDs, and the 29 pet is just not quite cutting it.<br>
<br>
It sounds like you are doing all the right things though.   I am impressed that you are tanking some for your pet and getting that Phantom Armor regen into play.   Darn good and efficient tactics.<br>
<br>
34 will be a whole new world for you.   Your power, and I kid you not, will <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> double</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->.   You get a new DD (Blaze), a new hard hitting bolt (Cinder), and new pets that look bigger. Your DD spells and bolts in the 34~38 time will outdamage all classes, including Wizzies.  The 34 pet is a darn good tank.  You can even use it a primary tank in an all-caster group.  34 is a great time as a Mage -- your raw power blows away all classes at this time.  IMO <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
